#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:84
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Variant Creation Mode` field informs Odoo when to "
"automatically create a new variant once an attribute is added to a product."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:88
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Variant Creation Mode` field **must** be set "
"to :guilabel:`Never` in order for the :guilabel:`Multi-checkbox` to work "
"properly as the :guilabel:`Display Type`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:91
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Instantly`: Creates all possible variants as soon as attributes "
"and values are added to a product template."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`तुरंत`: जैसे ही प्रॉडक्ट टेम्प्लेट में एट्रिब्यूट और वैल्यू जोड़े जाते हैं, सभी संभावित "
"वेरिएंट बनाता है।"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:93
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Dynamically`: Creates variants **only** when corresponding "
"attributes and values are added to a sales order."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`डायनामिकली`: वेरिएंट **सिर्फ़** तभी बनाता है जब सेल्स ऑर्डर में संबंधित "
"एट्रिब्यूट और वैल्यू जोड़ी जाती हैं।"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:95
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Never`: Prevents the automatic creation of purchaseable variants "
"with this tag. Instead, this tag is treated as being informational. If more "
"than one value is assigned to an attribute with this tag, all values are "
"loaded when the product displays, since the creation of discrete variants is "
"prevented."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`कभी नहीं`: इस टैग के साथ खरीदने योग्य वेरिएंट के ऑटोमैटिक क्रिएशन को रोकता है"
"। इसके बजाय, इस टैग को जानकारीपूर्ण माना जाता है। अगर इस टैग वाले एट्रिब्यूट को एक से "
"ज़्यादा वैल्यू असाइन की जाती हैं, तो प्रॉडक्ट डिस्प्ले होने पर सभी वैल्यू लोड हो जाती हैं, "
"क्योंकि अलग-अलग वेरिएंट का क्रिएशन रोका गया है।"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:101
msgid ""
"Once added to a product, an attribute's :guilabel:`Variants Creation Mode` "
"cannot be edited."
